          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Shortly after I leave the station I spot Jordan and Kayt walking two dogs towards me. It’s an enthusiastic greeting and fun chat to get us home, Kayte loves a joke and word play. I meet Felix at home and discuss his Raspberry Pi woes trying to bring life to his old CD collection. ",
